<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:11:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>苹果2024年伊始，巴克莱银行降级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</link><description>周二，巴克莱银行下调了这家全球市值最高公司的股价评级，原因是担心 2024 年从 iPhone 到 Mac 等苹果设备的需求仍将疲软，苹果股价下跌 3%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国打破高温记录，酷热天气从北到南烘烤城市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</link><description>2023年，中国的炎热天气有所缓解，从北京到上海的气温记录都被打破，这与同样席卷世界大部分地区的全球热浪现象相呼应，引发了人们对全球气候变化的更多担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，2023 年俄罗斯对欧洲的液化天然气出口量下降 1.9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russian-lng-exports-europe-fell-19-2023-lseg-data-2024-01-02/</link><description>伦敦证券交易所周二公布的数据显示，2023 年俄罗斯对欧洲的液化天然气 (LNG) 出口量下降 1.9%，至 1580 万吨，对亚洲的液化天然气出口量下降 11%，至 1490 万吨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/russian-lng-exports-europe-fell-19-2023-lseg-data-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：电子游戏规则引发骚乱后中国撤职官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-official-after-video-games-rules-spark-turmoil-sources-2024-01-02/</link><description>五位了解此事的消息人士称，中国解除了负责新闻出版监管机构的一名官员的职务，几天前，中国游戏股受到拟议的限制视频游戏支出规则的打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-removes-official-after-video-games-rules-spark-turmoil-sources-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：2024 年伊始，标普 500 指数将创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-02/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 11:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>2023 年全球工厂活动温和结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-global-factory-activity-ended-2023-soft-note-2024-01-02/</link><description>到 2023 年，全球工厂表现疲软，欧元区 12 月活动连续第 18 个月萎缩，亚洲制造业强国因中国经济复苏不稳而受到打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-global-factory-activity-ended-2023-soft-note-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，2023年中国国有开发商将主导销售和土地市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-owned-developers-dominate-sales-land-markets-2023-surveys-2024-01-02/</link><description>私人调查显示，随着越来越多的私营企业卷入该行业不断加深的债务危机，2023年中国房地产市场继续整合，国有企业主导了房屋销售和土地收购市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-owned-developers-dominate-sales-land-markets-2023-surveys-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰取消部分中国出口许可证后，阿斯麦股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-dip-after-netherlands-revokes-licence-some-china-exports-2024-01-02/</link><description>计算机芯片设备制造商ASML表示，荷兰政府已部分吊销其部分机器运往中国的出口许可证，导致该公司股价周二下跌，并遭到北京方面的批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-dip-after-netherlands-revokes-licence-some-china-exports-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国元旦假期房屋销量较2023年下降26%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-sales-during-new-year-holiday-fall-26-compared-with-2023-2024-01-02/</link><description>周二的一项调查显示，春节三天期间，中国40个城市的日均房屋销售面积（按建筑面积计算）与去年同期相比下降了26%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 08:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-sales-during-new-year-holiday-fall-26-compared-with-2023-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>与中国关系的争议使台湾竞选活动恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disputes-over-china-ties-sour-taiwan-election-campaign-2024-01-02/</link><description>关于如何处理与中国的关系并避免冲突的激烈争论正在台湾竞选活动的最后阶段占据主导地位，因为一些民意调查显示，台湾下一任总统的两位主要竞争者之间的竞争十分激烈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 06:46:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/disputes-over-china-ties-sour-taiwan-election-campaign-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>泰国和中国三月起互免公民签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-permanently-waive-visas-each-others-citizens-march-thai-pm-2024-01-02/</link><description>泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维信 (Srettha Thavisin) 周二表示，泰国和中国将从 3 月起永久免除对方公民的签证要求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-permanently-waive-visas-each-others-citizens-march-thai-pm-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>香港大亨黎智英在国家安全审判中不认罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-tycoon-jimmy-lai-pleads-not-guilty-national-security-trial-2024-01-02/</link><description>香港大亨和民主倡导者黎智英周二在一次具有里程碑意义的审判中表示不认罪，他被指控危害中国国家安全，检方详细说明了他们所说的与外国势力勾结的细节。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 03:52:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-tycoon-jimmy-lai-pleads-not-guilty-national-security-trial-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁台湾人民推动“和平统一”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-taiwans-people-promote-peaceful-reunification-2024-01-02/</link><description>中国国台办负责人周二呼吁台湾人民推动“和平统一”进程，称这是两岸人民的共同愿望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 03:25:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-taiwans-people-promote-peaceful-reunification-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济复苏脆弱，亚洲工厂 2023 年业绩疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factories-end-2023-soft-note-amid-fragile-china-recovery-2024-01-02/</link><description>12 月份亚洲工厂活动减弱，预示着该地区制造业强国 2024 年开局不稳，因为中国经济复苏的不平衡阻碍了需求的更广泛复苏。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 03:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factories-end-2023-soft-note-amid-fragile-china-recovery-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市回落，油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-02/</link><description>欧洲股市周二下跌，因交易员押注各国央行将在 2024 年降息，最初高开后走势发生变化，而红海海战后油价上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 02:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>